%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20also%20questioning%20representatives%20of%20the%20Kshatriya%20Seva%20Samithi%2C%20a%20local%20organisation%20from%20which%20Tulasi%20had%20sought%20help%20for%20her%20house%20construction.%20Tulasi%20had%20submitted%20an%20application%20to%20the%20Samithi%20for%20financial%20assistance%2C%20and%20they%20had%20previously%20sent%20her%20construction%20materials.%20The%20police%20are%20probing%20whether%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20crate%20was%20in%20any%20way%20connected%20to%20her%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20another%20twist%20to%20the%20story%2C%20Tulasi's%20son-in-law%20has%20been%20missing%20since%20the%20day%20the%20parcel%20was%20delivered.%20The%20police%20are%20investigating%20whether%20his%20disappearance%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20body.%20The%20cops%20are%20not%20ruling%20out%20a%20property%20dispute%20angle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734694380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fq1esci38_andhra-pradesh-woman_625x300_20_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwooden-crate-dead-body-a-letter-how-andhra-pradesh-womans-horror-unfolded-7293988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20received%20a%20wooden%20crate%20which%20she%20thought%20contained%20electrical%20goods%20for%20her%20new%20home.%20When%20she%20opened%20the%20crate%2C%20however%2C%20she%20found%20a%20dead%20body%20and%20a%20letter%20demanding%20Rs%201.35%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hungary%20sparks%20row%20with%20Poland%20by%20granting%20asylum%20to%20ex-minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734694378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fd093%2Flive%2F0dc18490-bebc-11ef-addc-4536c4252544.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9dp61weeggo%230%22%