0have%20not%20played%20in%20Pakistan%20since%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20captain%20Wasim%20Bari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20only%20imagine%20the%20warm%20welcome%20and%20hospitality%20their%20players%20and%20fans%20would%20get%20in%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%20Moin%20Khan%2C%20another%20former%20Pakistan%20skipper%2C%20too%20seemed%20glad%20with%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20PCB%20has%20been%20able%20to%20also%20get%20another%20ICC%20event%20to%20host%20it%20is%20good%20news%20for%20Pakistan%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Moin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20spinner%20Iqbal%20Qasim%20has%20praised%20the%20PCB%20for%20getting%20the%20ICC%2C%20BCCI%20and%20the%20ICC%20board%20to%20agree%20on%20a%20compromise%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBCCI%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20and%20financially%20influential%20board.%20But%20unlike%20last%20year's%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20this%20time%20our%20board%20took%20a%20stance%2C%20and%20gained%20something.%20Main%20thing%20is%20we%20are%20hosting%20the%20tournament%20and%20will%20also%20not%20go%20to%20India%20now%20to%20play%20in%20ICC%20events.%20Both%20teams%20will%20now%20play%20at%20neutral%20venues.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734693180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F72e7t908_t20-world-cup-2024-india-vs-pakistan-_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpcb-gained-more-than-bcci-after-iccs-compromise-formula-on-champions-trophy-pakistan-legends-mega-dig-7292579%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20and%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20agreed%20to%20play%20all%20India-Pakistan%20matches%20in%20neutral%20v