%2C%20which%20is%20just%20700%20metres%20from%20the%20site%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20where%20he%20is%20holding%20his%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dallewal%20has%20been%20on%20an%20indefinite%20fast%20since%20November%2026%20to%20press%20the%20Centre%20to%20accept%20the%20demands%20of%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20informed%20the%20court%20that%2C%20with%20Mr%20Dallewal's%20cooperation%2C%20an%20echocardiogram%20(ECG)%20and%20blood%20and%20other%20tests%20have%20been%20conducted%20and%20his%20health%20appears%20to%20be%20stable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Punjab%20government%20should%20take%20a%20call%20on%20admitting%20him%20(Mr%20Dallewal)%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Ensuring%20his%20stable%20health%20is%20the%20constitutional%20duty%20and%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Punjab%20government.%20His%20health%20should%20be%20constantly%20monitored%20and%20arrangements%20should%20be%20made%20accordingly.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20General%20Singh%20also%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20secretary%20has%20constituted%20a%20panel%20of%20doctors%20to%20monitor%20Mr%20Dallewal's%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20set%20January%202%20as%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing%20and%20asked%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20secretary%20and%20the%20medical%20superintendent%20of%20the%20makeshift%20hospital%20to%20submit%20an%20affidavit%20by%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20'jatha'%20(group)%20of%20101%20farmers%20had%20to%20call%20off%20their%20march%20to%20Delhi%20to%20press%20their%20demands%20for%20the%20third%20time%20on%20December%2014%20after%20tear%20gas%20and%20water%20cannons%20were%20used%2C%20injuring%20at%20least%2010%20of%20them.%20Two%20other%20attempts%20had%20to%20be%20similarly%20abandoned%20on%20Dece