mortgages%2Ffixed-rate-mortgage-vs-adjustable-rate-mortgage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efixed-rate%20vs.%20adjustable-rate%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARMs%20often%20(but%20not%20always)%20start%20with%20lower%20rates%20than%20fixed-rate%20mortgages%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Farm-rates-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EARM%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20change%20once%20your%20fixed-rate%20introductory%20period%20is%20over.%20If%20you%20plan%20on%20moving%20or%20refinancing%20before%20the%20rate%20adjusts%2C%20an%20ARM%20could%20be%20a%20good%20deal.%20But%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20change%20in%20circumstances%20could%20prevent%20you%20from%20doing%20these%20things%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20think%20about%20whether%20your%20budget%20could%20handle%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFixed-rate%20mortgages%20are%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20borrowers%20who%20want%20stability%2C%20since%20your%20monthly%20principal%20and%20interest%20payments%20won't%20change%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%20(though%20your%20mortgage%20payment%20could%20increase%20if%20your%20taxes%20or%20insurance%20go%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20stability%2C%20you%20may%20get%20a%20higher%20rate.%20This%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20deal%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20rates%20increase%20further%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20might%20be%20glad%20to%20have%20a%20rate%20locked%20in.%20And%20if%20rates%20trend%20down%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20to%20snag%20a%20lower%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1083101-35eb-4698-94bb-c0225c0d063d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Conventional%20vs.%20Government-Backed%20Mortgages%5C%22%3EConventional%20vs.%20Government-Backed%20Mortgages%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fconventional-mortgage%5C%2