v%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F4bbeo46g_rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat_160x120_01_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20K.B.%20Hedgewar%20to%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way.%20It's%20a%20miraculous%20journey%20of%20a%20hundred%20years%20now.%20It%20has%20faced%20three%20bans%2C%20social%20ostracisation%2C%20and%20also%20the%20accusation%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20Gandhi's%20assassination.%20But%20it%20has%20always%20bounced%20back%20with%20a%20vengeance.%20The%20RSS%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20a%20formidable%20organisation%2C%20aspiring%20to%20make%20India%20great%20again.%20In%20its%20arduous%20journey%2C%20the%20RSS%20has%20seen%20six%20full-time%20Sarsanghchalaks%2C%20with%20different%20temperaments%20and%20personalities%20but%20with%20one%20goal%3A%20to%20make%20India%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20If%20Hedgewar%20was%20a%20former%20congressman%20who%20felt%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpain%20of%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%20and%20realised%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20Hindus%20have%20to%20be%20saved%20from%20future%20humiliation%20as%20they%20had%20suffered%20in%20the%20past%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20unite%20and%20organise%E2%80%9D%2C%20then%20Golwalkar%20should%20be%20credited%20with%20ensuring%20that%20the%20RSS%20sailed%20through%20its%20most%20turbulent%20times%20with%20an%20iron%20will%20and%20conviction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Hedgewar%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20Hindu%20unity%20project%2C%20it%20was%20Golwalkar%20who%20built%20the%20structure%20with%20solid%20ideological%20cement.%20Unlike%20Golwalkar%2C%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%20was%20more%20political.%20He%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20political%20force.%20Rajendra%20Singh%20and%20K.S.%20Sudarshan%20helped%20consolidate%20the%20gains%20made%20during%20Deoras's%20time.%20Bhagwat%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20displayed%20the%20maturity%20to%20anoint%20Modi%20as%20Advani's%20successor%20and%20allow%20him%20to%20lead%20the%20movement%20with%20a%20cult%20following.%20However%2C%20what%20is%20often%20overlooked%20about%20him%20is%20that%2C%20like%20Deoras%2C%20he%20is%20a%20reformist.%20He%20is%20not%20one%20to%20cling%20to%20the%20past.%20He%20possesses%20the%20guile%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20farsightedness%20to%20envision%20the%20future%20and%20introduce%20bold%2C%20transformative%20changes%20to%20the%20ideological%20stream%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20without%20compromising%20its%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhagwat%2C%20The%20Reformer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Bhagwat%20has%20taken%20on%20the%20toughest%20job%20among%20all%20the%20RSS%20chiefs.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20he%20must%20carefully%20navigate%20his%20relationship%20with%20a%20powerful%20figure%20like%20Modi%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20he%20must%20engage%20in%20ideological%20engineering%20within%20Hindutva.%20He%20is%20tasked%20with%20managing%20the%20raw%20energy%20of%20a%20cadre%20that%20is%20experiencing%20unbridled%20power%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Throughout%20this%20journey%2C%20he%20has%20endured%20so%20much%2C%20yet%20never%20wavered.%20He%20was%20labelled%20the%20weakest%20RSS%20chief%20and%20criticised%20for%20compromising%20the%20original%20thesis%20of%20Hindutva%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Hindus%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20winning%20a%20decisive%20battle%20with%20Muslims%20in%20a%201%2C200-year-old%20civilisational%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20political%20pundits%20forget%20that%20long%20before%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20shambles.%20When%20Bhagwat%20took%20over%20from%20Sudarshan%2C%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20was%20grappling%20with%20ideological%20confusion.%20The%20BJP%20was%20in%20shock%20after%20its%20surprising%20loss%20in%202004.%20The%20Atal-Advani%20duo%20was%20pushing%20for%20a%20more%20moderate%20and%20liberal%20face%20for%20the%20party%2C%20while%20it%20was%20still%20reeling%20from%20Advani's%20Jinnah%20blunder.%20There%20was%20no%20harmony%20between%20the%20RSS%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20its%20other%20affiliate%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EChoosing%20Modi%20Over%20Gadkari%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20becoming%20the%20RSS%20chief%20in%202007%2C%20Bhagwat%20waited%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%202009%20elections.%20Once%20he%20was%20convinced%20that%20the%20Atal-Advani%20era%20had%20ended%20and%20the%20BJP%20needed%20fresh%20blood%20to%20navigate%20through%20troubled%20waters%2C%20he%20came%20to%20Delhi%2C%20settled%20at%20Keshav%20Kunj%20in%20Jhandewalan%2C%20and%20boldly%20stated%20that%20the%20new%20party%20president%20would%20not%20be%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CGang%20of%20Four%E2%80%9D%20(Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%2C%20and%20Anant%20Kumar).%20He%20chose%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20much%20younger%20than%20the%20Delhi-based%20leaders%20and%20then%20a%20virtual%20non-entity%20in%20Delhi%20politics.%20Gadkari%20was%20groomed%20as%20the%20party's%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20for%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20but%20when%20corruption%20charges%20emerged%20against%20him%2C%20Bhagwat%20acted%20swiftly%2C%20replacing%20him%20with%20Modi%E2%80%94a%20move%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20masterstroke.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%20Bhagwat%20realised%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20win%20in%202014%2C%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20movement%20would%20be%20in%20jeopardy.%20Among%20all%20the%20BJP%20chief%20ministers%2C%20Modi%20not%20only%20had%20the%20resources%20but%20also%20the%20ideological%20clarity%20that%20the%20BJP%20should%20not%20waver%20from%20its%20core%20ideology%E2%80%94Hindutva.%20Modi's%20gladiatorial%20instincts%20and%20Amit%20Shah's%20organisational%20skills%20transformed%20the%20BJP%20into%20an%20unmatched%20political%20machine.%20However%2C%20under%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20also%20earned%20a%20bad%20reputation%20due%20to%20the%20ultra-aggressive%20Hindutva.%20Muslims%20have%20been%20unabashedly%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Course-Correction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20Bhagwat%20opposed%20the%20march%20of%20aggressive%20Hindutva%2C%20but%20he%20realised%20that%20if%20the%20anti-Muslim%20campaign%20continued%20unchecked%2C%20the%20terms%20%E2%80%9CHindutva%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CHindu%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20discredited%20globally%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20undoing%20of%20the%20RSS's%20entire%20Hindu%20project.%20He%20was%20also%20concerned%20about%20the%20deep%20societal%20polarisation%20over%20Hindu-Muslim%20issues.%20He%20understood%20that%20a%20population%20of%2020%20crore%20Muslims%20was%20too%20large%20to%20push%20to%20the%20brink%20without%20consequences.%20Once%20this%20realisation%20dawned%20on%20him%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20first%20slow%20down%20the%20process%20of%20Islamophobia%20and%2C%20later%2C%20tame%20the%20beast%20of%20unruly%2C%20self-proclaimed%20Hindutva%20warriors.%20He%20took%20a%20risk.%20While%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20Vigyan%20Bhawan%20in%202018%2C%20he%20boldly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20Muslims%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20incomplete.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20shook%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade.%20Many%20of%20them%20privately%20told%20me%20that%20it%20had%20not%20been%20well%20received%20by%20the%20cadre%2C%20who%20had%20been%20trained%20to%20hate%20Muslims.%20One%20senior%20RSS%20member%20even%20told%20me%20that%20he%20would%20sit%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Edharna%20%3C%2Fem%3Eif%20Bhagwat%20continued%20with%20this%20line%20of%20thinking.%20But%20Bhagwat%20did%20not%20stop.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20DNA%20of%20everyone%20living%20in%20India%20is%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%20When%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2FBabri%20Masjid%20issue%2C%20he%20asked%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20celebrated%20as%20a%20victory.%20He%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Muslim%20leaders%20and%20intellectuals.%20He%20visited%20Deoband%20to%20meet%20Arshad%20Madni%2C%20a%20highly%20respected%20leader%20in%20the%20Muslim%20world%20and%20promised%20him%20that%20one%20day%20he%20would%20invite%20him%20to%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20in%20Varanasi%20to%20determine%20if%20it%20had%20been%20built%20over%20a%20temple%2C%20he%20politely%20disapproved%20of%20the%20entire%20exercise.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20hunt%20for%20a%20Shivling%20in%20every%20mosque%3F%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20the%20observation%20by%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20that%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%201991%20did%20not%20prevent%20the%20ascertaining%20of%20the%20character%20of%20a%20religious%20place%2C%20opened%20the%20floodgates%20for%20such%20petitions.%20Courts%2C%20in%20their%20enthusiasm%2C%20not%20only%20admitted%20these%20petitions%20but%20also%20ordered%20surveys.%20Such%20court%20orders%20led%20to%20violence%20and%20loss%20of%20life%20in%20Sambhal.%20Even%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20was%20not%20spared.%20Somehow%2C%20good%20sense%20prevailed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20it%20has%20temporarily%20halted%20this%20process%20until%20the%20final%20verdict%20is%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Bhagwat%20has%20intervened%20once%20again.%20Speaking%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Ram%20temple%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20faith%2C%20and%20Hindus%20felt%20that%20it%20should%20be%20built.%20Raising%20issues%20about%20some%20new%20sites%20out%20of%20hate%20and%20enmity%20is%20unacceptable.%E2%80%9D%20Bhagwat's%20statement%20should%20be%20welcomed%20by%20all%2C%20regardless%20of%20faith%20or%20political%20affiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGood%20Intentions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20know%20many%20will%20question%20his%20assertion%20and%20impute%20motives.%20Some%20may%20argue%20that%20Bhagwat%20is%20engaging%20in%20a%20deception%20game.%20There%20is%20some%20merit%20to%20this%20argument.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20despite%20Bhagwat's%20statements%2C%20there%20was%20no%20respite%20from%20the%20hate%20campaign%20and%20Muslim-bashing%20by%20Hindutva%20forces.%20However%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20Bhagwat%20should%20be%20given%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt.%20Court%20cases%20in%20such%20matters%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20set%20society%20on%20fire%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20violence.%20Sambhal%20is%20just%20one%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20do%20not%20doubt%20Bhagwat's%20intent.%20I%20believe%20he%20realises%20that%20this%20is%20a%20dangerous%20game%20and%20the%20country%20could%20be%20in%20flames%20in%20no%20time%20if%20the%20fanatics%20are%20not%20stopped.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20change%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20movement%20whose%20DNA%20is%20defined%20by%20anti-Islam%20rhetoric%20and%20a%20hate%20campaign%20against%20Muslims%2C%20one%20that%20believes%20Hindus%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%201%2C200-year%20war%20with%20Islam.%20But%20if%20he%20is%20genuinely%20trying%20to%20stop%20this%20madness%2C%20it%20is%20a%20welcome%20sign.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20he%20is%20riding%20a%20ferocious%20tiger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734691080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F4bbeo46g_rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat_160x120_01_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt