e%20Christmas%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20lower%20their%20expectations%20regarding%20future%20gifts.%20I%20told%20them%20about%20my%20financial%20situation%2C%20what%20I%20could%20spend%20on%2C%20and%20what%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20accomplish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpending%20exorbitant%20amounts%20on%20Christmas%20was%20out%20of%20the%20question.%20Being%20open%20and%20honest%20about%20my%20struggles%20and%20primary%20issues%20worked%20out%20in%20my%20favor.%20I%20wasn't%20nervous%20to%20have%20this%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20them%20understood%2C%20and%20I%20was%20truly%20relieved%20once%20I%20confessed.%20It%20immediately%20broke%20the%20needless%20superficial%20confinement%20I%20had%20put%20myself%20in%20to%20conform%20to%20the%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f2e70dc-10ef-46d1-b82a-d734841ed44d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20also%20prepared%20myself%20to%20receive%20less%20of%20what%20I%20had%20previously%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20family%20members%20would%20still%20buy%20me%20costly%20gifts%2C%20some%20limited%20their%20splurging%20on%20me%20after%20this%20conversation.%20I%20was%20satisfied%20with%20getting%20whatever%20they%20would%20get%20me%2C%20even%20if%20it%20was%20nothing%20sometimes.%20Some%20even%20joined%20me%20in%20setting%20this%20boundary%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20enjoying%20Christmas%20even%20more%20without%20having%20to%20impress%20people%20with%20my%20gift-giving%20superpowers.%20I%20became%20accustomed%20to%20speaking%20my%20mind%20and%20being%20truthful%20at%20all%20times.%20When%20you%20embrace%20life%20in%20that%20manner%2C%20many%20burdens%20are%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228df1ebf7-db35-4009-8064-1662807d022b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20as%20I%20make%20more%20money%2C%20gifts%20still%20don't%20seem%20important%20to%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20financial%20situation%20has%20improved%2C%20but%20I%20now%20sometimes%20only%20ha