%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661803351caec1275a6f24ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20student-debt%20cancellation%20for%20borrowers%20in%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness.%3Cp%3EKyle%20Mazza%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20announced%20%244.28%20billion%20in%20student-debt%20cancellation%20for%2054%2C900%20borrowers%20in%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20relief%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Education%20Department's%20ongoing%20fixes%20to%20PSLF.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20unlikely%20to%20continue%20Biden's%20student-debt%20relief%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20announced%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-pslf-borrowers-getting-debt-cancellation-biden-relief-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20one%20month%20left%20until%20he%20leaves%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Biden%20and%20his%20Education%20Department%20said%20they%20have%20approved%20%244.28%20billion%20in%20student%20debt%20for%2054%2C900%20borrowers%20in%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relief%20is%20a%20result%20of%20ongoing%20improvements%20to%20PSLF%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattorneys-general-biden-extend-pslf-waiver-student-debt-confusion-harm-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaiver%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20expired%20in%20October%202022%20that%20allowed%20payments%20that%20previously%20did%20not%20qualify%20for%20relief%20to%20count%20toward%2