20that%2C%208%20million%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Biden's%20new%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20intended%20to%20make%20monthly%20payments%20cheaper%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20forgiveness%20%E2%80%94%20are%20in%20limbo%20as%20they%20wait%20for%20a%20court%20to%20decide%20if%20the%20plan%20can%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Biden's%20plans%20for%20broader%20relief%20do%20survive%20their%20legal%20challenges%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20Trump's%20administration%20would%20continue%20those%20efforts.%20Preston%20Cooper%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative-leaning%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-cheaper-student-loan-payments-trump-debt-relief-biden-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bhas%20taken%20a%20stance%20of%2C%20'We%20want%20to%20try%20and%20forgive%20as%20much%20debt%20as%20possible%20through%20various%20different%20programs.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20put%20it%20mildly%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20see%20that%20same%20attitude%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20proposed%20eliminating%20PSLF%20during%20his%20first%20term%2C%20but%20doing%20so%20requires%20congressional%20approval.%20Republican%20control%20of%20Congress%20and%20the%20White%20House%20means%20that%20Trump%20would%20likely%20have%20more%20success%20achieving%20his%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Day%20One%20of%20my%20Administration%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20higher%20education%20is%20a%20ticket%20to%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20not%20a%20barrier%20to%20opportunity%2C%26qu