ministration%20has%20issued%20an%20urgent%20warning%20on%20arthritis%20medication%20Librela%2C%20which%20is%20commonly%20being%20used%20to%20treat%20osteoarthritis%20in%20dogs.%20This%20injectable%20drug%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20severe%20side%20effects%20such%20as%20seizures%2C%20lameness%2C%20and%20loss%20of%20muscle%20control%2C%20which%20could%20potentially%20risk%20the%20health%20of%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20January%202023%20and%20March%202024%2C%20over%203%2C600%20adverse%20health%20reactions%20have%20been%20reported%2C%20some%20of%20which%20may%20have%20been%20fatal.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fanimal-veterinary%2Fproduct-safety-information%2Fdear-veterinarian-letter-notifying-veterinarians-about-adverse-events-reported-dogs-treated-librela%5C%22%3EThe%20FDA%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20issued%20a%20warning%2C%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20to%20pet%20owners%2C%20cautioning%20them%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20dangers%20posed%20by%20Librela%2C%20which%20could%20severely%20impact%20the%20health%20of%20affected%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPet%20owners%20should%20seek%20advice%20from%20veterinarians%20for%20alternative%20treatment%20plans%20and%20closely%20monitor%20their%20pets%20for%20signs%20of%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adverse%20events%20identified%20and%20analysed%20include%20ataxia%2C%20seizures%2C%20and%20other%20neurologic%20signs%2C%20including%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20paresis%2C%20recumbency%2C%20urinary%20incontinence%2C%20polyuria%2C%20and%20polydipsia.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20death%20(including%20euthanasia)%20was%20reported%20as%20an%20outcome%20of%20these%20adverse%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fanimal-veterinary%2Fproduct-safety-information%2Fdear-veterinarian-letter-notifying-veterinarians-about-adverse-events-reported-dogs-treated-librela%5C%22%3Eagency%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrug%20Information%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fanimal-veterinary%2Fproduct-safety-information%2Fdear-veterinarian-letter-notifying-veterinarians-about-adverse-events-reported-dogs-treated-librela%5C%22%3EFDA%20%3C%2Fa%3Eapproved%20Librela%2C%20a%20monoclonal%20antibody%20drug%20used%20for%20the%20control%20of%20pain%20associated%20with%20osteoarthritis%20in%20dogs%2C%20on%20May%205%2C%202023%2C%20and%20it%20was%20introduced%20to%20the%20marketplace%20later%20that%20year.%20Prior%20to%20approval%2C%20the%20FDA%20reviewed%20available%20studies%20and%20other%20data%20on%20Librela%20and%20determined%20Librela%20to%20be%20safe%20and%20effective%20for%20its%20intended%20use%20for%20control%20of%20pain%20associated%20with%20osteoarthritis%20in%20dogs.%20Librela%20is%20dosed%20by%20weight%20and%20labelled%20for%20subcutaneous%20injection%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20should%20a%20veterinarian%20do%20if%20a%20patient%20treated%20with%20Librela%20has%20an%20adverse%20event%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20dog%20under%20your%20care%20experiences%20an%20adverse%20event%20while%20receiving%20Librela%2C%20the%20FDA%20encourages%20you%20to%20report%20it%20to%20Zoetis%2C%20the%20drug%20sponsor%2C%20at%201-888-963-8471.%20Drug%20sponsors%20are%20required%20to%20submit%20reports%20of%20adverse%20drug%20events%20to%20the%20FDA.%20If%20you%20prefer%20to%20report%20directly%20to%20the%20FDA%2C%20please%20see%20www.fda.gov%2Freportanimalae.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20reporting%20adverse%20events%20to%20the%20FDA%20and%2For%20Zoetis%2C%20please%20include%2C%20if%20available%2C%20a%20full%20medical%20history%2C%20how%20many%20times%20the%20dog%20has%20received%20Librela%2C%20and%20the%20lot%20number%20on%20the%20vial%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734688380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhue33s8o_pet-owners_625x300_20_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpopular-dog-arthritis-medication-is-killing-them-says-report-7293136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20drug%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20severe%20side%20effects%20such%20as%20seizures%20and%20muscle%20control%20loss%2C%20with%20over%203%2C600%20adverse%20health%20reactions%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpopular-dog-arthritis-medication-is-killing-them-says-report-7293136%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Allu%20Arjun%20starrer%20Pushpa%202%20set%20to%20cross%20Rs%201000%20crore%20net%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734688376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116500461%2Cimgsize-50596.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fpushpa-2-box-office-collection-day-16-updated-live-the-allu-arjun-starrer-set-to-cross-rs-1000-crore-net-on-friday%2Farticleshow%2F116500538.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Pushpa%202'%20will%20cross%20Rs%201000%20crore%20at%20the%20box%20office%20in%20India%2C%20in%20all%20languages%20by%20the%20end%20of%20Friday.%20The%20film%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20good%20jump%20over%20the%20coming%20weekend%20which%20will%20be%20its%20third%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20ENTERTAINMENT%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fpushpa-2-box-office-collection-day-16-updated-live-the-allu-arjun-starrer-set-to-cross-rs-1000-crore-net-on-friday%2Farticleshow%2F116500538.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pushpa%202'%20box%20office%20collection%20day%2016%20(Updated%20Live)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734688376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsta