ess%20opportunity.%20Gillespie%20appears%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20freedom%2C%20however%2C%20to%20get%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20he%20has%20taken%20to%20interviewing%20the%20firm's%20executives%20using%20his%20iPhone%20in%20a%20series%20of%20walk-and-talk%20interviews%20the%20firm%20has%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BBetween%20Two%20Meetings.%26quot%3B%20In%20one%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQqJaCSy1xMk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepisode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gillespie%20catches%20the%20firm's%20head%20of%20private%20equity%2C%20Joe%20Baratta%2C%20in%20the%20hallway%20and%20asks%20about%20the%20company's%20portfolio%20of%20owned%20and%20operated%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20people%20filming%20in%20an%20office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6764959a1cee543535a86a71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20L%3A%20Matt%20Anderson%2C%20Laurie%20Carlson%2C%20and%20Jon%20Gray%20film%20a%20scene%20at%20Blackstone's%20NYC%20headquarters.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Nicoll%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Baratta%20starts%20to%20answer%2C%20a%20black%20bar%20with%20the%20word%20%26quot%3BREDACTED%26quot%3B%20appears%20over%20his%20mouth%2C%20and%20a%20closed%20caption%20appears%20on%20the%20bottom%3A%20%26quot%3BNOT%20APPROVED%20BY%20BLACKSTONE%20LEGAL%20AND%20COMPLIANCE.%26quot%3B%20The%20audio%20of%20Baratta%20speaking%20is%20replaced%20with%20some%20loungey%20bossa%20nova%20as%20he%20walks%20through%20the%20halls%20to%20the%20elevator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20(hopefully)%20walks%20away%20from%20that%20video%20chuckling%20at%20corporate%20America%2C%20but%20also%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20it%20is%20like%20to%20work%20at%20Blackstone.%20Before%20the%20censors%20cut%20him%20off%2C%20Baratta%20was%20explaining%20that%20he%20was%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20firm's%20%26quot%3Bweekly%20private-equity%20Monday%20morning%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20includes%20the%20entire%20team%20from%20around%20the%20globe.%20Schwarzman%20had%20been%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20Baratta%20says%2C%20telling%20them%20about%20his%20recent%20trip%20to%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20series%2C%20Gillespie's%20video%20team%20interviews%20a%20series%20of%20managing%20directors.%20It's%20shot%20with%20upbeat%20music%20and%20spiffy%20editing%20like%20something%20you%20might%20see%20on%20the%20Food%20Network's%20%26quot%3BDiners%2C%20Drive-Ins%2C%20and%20Dives.%26quot%3B%20The%20series%20seems%20geared%20toward%20highlighting%20Blackstone%20as%20a%20place%20to%20work%2C%20with%20questions%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20What%20qualities%20do%20you%20look%20for%20in%20junior%20employees%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20overcome%20a%20career%20setback%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGray%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20videos%20can%20help%20with%20recruiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20interviewing%20someone%20yesterday%20who%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20work%20here%20because%20of%20the%20holiday%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20Gray%20told%20BI%20while%20filming%20a%20scene%20for%20the%20holiday%20video.%20%26quot%3B'You%20guys%20know%20how%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20yourself.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShowing%20that%20you%20can%20laugh%20at%20yourself%20is%20an%20important%20%26quot%3Bhumanizing%26quot%3B%20touch%2C%20Gray%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20you're%20a%20human-scale%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BJon%20Gray's%20baby%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20its%20holiday%20video%20or%20its%20internal%20video%20team%2C%20but%20Anderson%20said%20the%20company%20is%20saving%20money%20with%20its%20approach%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20outside%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20realizing%20that%20by%20having%20an%20in-house%20team%2C%20you%20could%20produce%20this%20stuff%20so%20much%20more%20efficiently%20and%20cheaply%2C%20and%20then%20you%20could%20just%20use%20this%20stuff%20for%20more%20moments%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20BI%20reporter%20watched%20the%20filming%20of%20a%20few%20scenes%20adding%20up%20to%2045%20seconds%20in%20the%20final%20video.%20It%20took%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20to%20film%20these%20scenes%2C%20with%20a%20coterie%20of%20video%20and%20marketing%20professionals%20on%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20cowboy%20hat%20watches%20another%20man%20on%20mkeshift%20horse%20in%20front%20of%20a%20green%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676498876c531c315b897a26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteve%20Schwarzman%20watches%20Jay%20Gillespie%20ride%20a%20makeshift%20horse%20for%20the%202024%20Blackstone%20holiday%20video.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Nicoll%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20professional%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20both%20Blackstone%20and%20other%20financial%20institutions%20confirmed%20much%20of%20what%20Blackstone's%20executives%20said%20about%20their%20video-production%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20person%2C%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20to%20protect%20career%20opportunities%2C%20said%20Blackstone%20differs%20from%20other%20financial%20firms%20in%20its%20decision%20to%20forgo%20a%20costly%20production%20studio%20in%20favor%20of%20a%20team%20that%20shoots%20from%20wherever%20they%20can%20within%20the%20office.%20The%20end%20product%20takes%20viewers%20inside%20the%20firm's%20hallways%20and%20executives'%20offices%2C%20giving%20the%20videos%20a%20documentary%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20professional%20said%20too%20many%20financial%20firms%20are%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20make%20one%20room%20with%20four%20walls%20look%20interesting.%26quot%3B%20They%20also%20said%20few%20financial%20firms%20have%20realized%20the%20benefits%20of%20investing%20in%20full-time%20video%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20person%20referred%20to%20Blackstone's%20holiday%20video%20as%20%26quot%3BJon%20Gray's%20baby%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20Gray%20appears%20to%20have%20a%20great%20working%20relationship%20with%20Gillespie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20met%20and%20had%20a%20meeting%20of%20minds%20and%20just%20got%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20this%20person%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20brainstorm%20very%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGillespie%20credited%20Gray%20and%20Anderson%20with%20having%20the%20vision%20to%20invest%20in%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20if%20you're%20not%20fluent%20in%20video%20these%20days%2C%20you're%20missing%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Jon%20and%20Christine%20caught%20that%20really%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGray%20is%20usually%20the%20first%20person%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20holiday%20video%2C%20Gillespie%20said.%20Sometime%20in%20the%20early%20summer%2C%20Gray%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20Gillespie%20and%20Anderson%20with%20some%20themes.%20Then%2C%20Gillespie%2C%20Gray%2C%20and%20Anderson%20work%20together%20on%20the%20script%20before%20shooting%20starts%20later%20in%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20firm's%20first%20holiday%20party%20in%201985%2C%20which%20included%20just%20nine%20people%2C%20Schwarzman%20told%20BI.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20new%20approach%2C%20the%20firm's%20billionaire%20founder%20took%20a%20philosophical%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20your%20home%20and%20this%20is%20where%20you%20spend%20more%20time%20than%20you%20do%20at%20your%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20while%20decked%20out%20in%20a%2010-gallon%20hat%20between%20video%20shoots.%20%26quot%3BSo%