y%2C%20perpetuated%20by%20exploitative%20middlemen%20and%20inadequate%20support%20systems%2C%20casts%20a%20long%20shadow%20over%20rural%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20growing%20peanuts%20for%20several%20decades%2C%2065-year-old%20Ram%20Khilawan%20is%20often%20left%20with%20poor%20yields%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20access%20to%20quality%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20buy%20seeds%20from%20the%20market%2C%20but%20the%20quality%20is%20poor%2C%20so%20the%20peanuts%20don%E2%80%99t%20grow%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20we%20get%20for%20them%20is%20dismal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20agrarian%20gloom%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20entrepreneur%20from%20Unnao%2C%20Aman%20Kumar%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98nutty%E2%80%99%20idea%20and%20a%20relentless%20spirit%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20computer%20applications%20degree%20in%20hand%2C%20Aman%20graduated%20in%202016%2C%20ready%20to%20embark%20on%20his%20professional%20journey.%20However%2C%20unsure%20of%20his%20next%20steps%2C%20he%20ventured%20into%20the%20global%20market%2C%20taking%20on%20freelance%20web%20design%20and%20development%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20exposed%20me%20to%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20business%20world%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20that%20bug%20of%20entrepreneurship%20was%20set%20in%20my%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20an%20MBA%2C%20preparing%20diligently%20for%20the%20CAT%20exam.%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20into%20Symbiosis%20College%20in%20Pune%2C%20but%20the%20fee%20was%20too%20high%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to