24%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-1200x1600.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528.jpeg%201320w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EA%20farmer%20harvests%20peanuts%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20carefully%20pulling%20the%20plants%20to%20collect%20the%20fresh%20crop%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20has%20witnessed%20remarkable%20growth%20in%20recent%20years.%20Revenue%20surged%20from%20Rs%2060%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20in%202023%2C%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20Rs%2013-15%20lakh%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20collaboration%20and%20innovative%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20getting%20better%20prices%20for%20each%20kilogram%20of%20peanuts%20we%20sell%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20see%20a%20real%20improvement%20in%20our%20seasonal%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aditya%20Sengar%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20world%2C%20and%20studied%20these%20things%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20bring%20in%20fresh%20ideas%20to%20farming%2C%20learn%20about%20modern%20techniques%2C%20and%20open%20up%20new%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20expand%20their%20impact%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20is%20collaborating%20with%20the%20Chief%20Development%20Officer%20to%20map%20500%20hectares%20of%20land%20for%20a%20proposed%20peanut%20farming%20cluster.%20This%20initiative%20will%20not%20only%20provide%20farmers%20with%20recognition%20but%20also%20offer%20crucial%20support%20services.%20Once%20recognised%20as%20a%20cluster%2C%20farmers%20will%20gain%20better%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20strengthening%20their%20position%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20achieve%20greater%20prosperity.%20Currently%2C%20the%20producer%20group%20comprises%2050%20farmers%2C%20but%20the%20ambitious%20cluster%20development%20plan%20aims%20to%20unite%202%2C000%20farmers%2C%20creating%20a%20powerful%20collective%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20issue%20we%20see%20around%20the%20world%20is%20that%20farmers%20aren%E2%80%99t%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352547%2Ffarmers-income-aneesh-jain-gram-unnati-value-chain-rajasthan-agri-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efair%20price%20for%20their%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20peanuts%20%E2%80%94%20whatever%20they%20grow%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20fair%20price.%20This%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20pain%20points%20we%E2%80%99ve%20observed.%20We%E2%80%99re%20not%20claiming%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20fixed%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20within%20our%20capacity%2C%20we%20are%20helping%20farmers%20mobilise%2C%20create%20clusters%2C%20and%20secure%20the%20incentives%20that%20are%20put%20in%20place%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20Image%20courtesy%20Aman%20Kumar%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734618600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.25-PM-1_11zon-1734607494-1536x2048.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D390877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aman%20Kumar%20at%20Nutty%20Village%20in%20Unnao%20is%20helping%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20peanut%20farmers%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20the%20resources%2C%20market%20access%2C