t%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Zero-energy%20low-cost%20cold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20in%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20West%20Khasi%20Hills%20struggle%20with%20warehousing%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20logistics.%20The%20lack%20of%20affordable%2C%20energy-efficient%20storage%20solutions%20for%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20often%20results%20in%20significant%20post-harvest%20losses%20and%20reduced%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20small%20project%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20the%20non-profit%20driving%20this%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%20So%20far%2C%20three%20units%20have%20been%20constructed%20in%20different%20villages%2C%20each%20costing%20Rs%201.64%20lakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NSSS%20works%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20community%20in%20several%20areas%20like%20farming%2C%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20child%20services.%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20projects%20for%20farmers.%20I%20mobilise%20farmers%20and%20also%20help%20them%20access%20assistance%20from%20government%20and%20private%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20these%20storage%20units%20came%20from%20the%20farmers%20themselves.%20Struggling%20to%20store%20their%20produce%2C%20they%20faced%20losses%20even%20before%20reaching%20the%20markets%2C%20compounded%20by%20low%20prices.%20While%20the%20project%20began%20in%202019%2C%20its%20progress%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSSS%20oversees%20the%20construction%20of%20these%20units%20by%20hiring%20contractors%2C%20using%20locally%20available%20materials%20like%20burned%20bricks%2C%20river%20sand%2C%20bamboo%20poles%2C%20CGI%20sheets%2C%20iron%20nails%2C%20cement%2C%20and%20pebbles.%20Each%20unit%20can%20store%20up%20to%20a%20tonne%20of%20produce%2C%20preserving%20it%20for%20one%20to%20four%20weeks.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20units%20are%20quick%20to%20construct%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20just%20a%20day%20or%20two%20%E2%80%94%20and%20require%20no%20maintenance.%20Farmers%20can%20use%20them%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20fill%20the%20gap%20between%20two%20layers%20of%20the%20structure%20with%20river%20sand%20and%20pebbles.%20This%20sand%20is%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%20This%20keeps%20the%20produce%20cool.%20Each%20unit%20benefits%20over%20120%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388012%